text: Sophie Hennebert (born 1904, date of death unknown) was a Belgian diver. She competed in the women's 10 metre platform event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1904 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Belgian female divers Category:Olympic divers of Belgium Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
